      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis index prediction vs. in-vitro benchmark — nominal operating point",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (nIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic pump at 5000 RPM, 6 L/min. Mean absolute error 12.3%; within MRL 5 acceptance band of 15% at 95th percentile confidence interval."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vad-vr-002",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Velocity field PIV comparison — impeller exit plane",
      "description": "Simulated velocity magnitude at impeller exit compared with particle image velocimetry data. RMS deviation 8.7% of peak velocity; spatial correlation coefficient 0.94 across 1200 interrogation windows."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vad-vr-003",
