      "name": "Pressure rise vs. flow curve — 3500 to 6000 RPM sweep",
      "description": "Predicted hydraulic head matches experimental pump curve within 5.1% across the full operating envelope. Validation performed at five speed setpoints and seven flow rates per setpoint."
    }
